text: Oulens-sur-Lucens was a municipality in the district Broye-Vully in the canton of Vaud in Switzerland. On 1 July 2011 it became part of the municipality of Lucens.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 17 February 2011 == References == Category:Former municipalities of Vaud Category:Villages in Vaud Category:2011 disestablishments in Switzerland
title: Oulens-sur-Lucens
